OL,7,FTens of thousands of illicit
OL,8,Fcigarettes and vapes have been seized
OL,9,Fafter officers discovered a concealed
OL,10,Floft space between two shops and a
OL,11,Fflat in Gateshead.
OL,13,FPolice and Trading Standards officers
OL,14,Fexecuted a warrant on Rawling Road in
OL,15,FBensham on Wednesday 3 April.
