OL,4,Ccigarettes found in hidden shop loft
OL,5,Cspace
OL,7,FOfficers found 27,200 illicit
OL,8,Fcigarettes, 8.5kg of illicit hand-
OL,9,Frolled tobacco as well as 63 illegal
OL,10,Fvapes. #350 in cash was also taken
OL,11,Ffrom one of the shop's tills and a
OL,12,Fcard reading machine.
OL,14,FIt is believed the total value of the
OL,15,Fhaul is between #15,000 and #20,000.
OL,17,FIt's believed the space between the
OL,18,Ftwo stores was being used to pass
OL,19,Fillicit products.
