OL,7,FThe action was part of the ongoing
OL,8,FOperation Vienna which was established
OL,9,Fseveral years ago and sees police work
OL,10,Fwith local authorities to share
OL,11,Fintelligence in the aim of minimising
OL,12,Fcrime, disorder and anti-social
OL,13,Fbehaviour.
