OL,5,Cspace
OL,7,FSpeaking about the operation,
OL,8,FInspector Gillian Menzies, of
OL,9,FNorthumbria Police, said: "The
OL,10,Foperation was launched so that we have
OL,11,Fa robust and effective plan in place
OL,12,Fto tackle criminality in Bensham and
OL,13,Fwe're pleased to see that it continues
OL,14,Fto uncover illicit items which should
OL,15,Fnot be for sale in any premises.
OL,17,F"As the public can see, we are not
OL,18,Fstopping targeting these gangs even
OL,19,Fthough we continue to find even more
OL,20,Fsophisticated concealments in shops.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
