OL,3,CTens of thousands of illicit
OL,4,Ccigarettes found in hidden shop loft
OL,5,Cspace
OL,7,F"No one in any of our communities
OL,8,Fshould have to tolerate criminality
OL,9,Fand as a Force we will do all we can
OL,10,Fto tackle it, acting on any
OL,11,Finformation supplied to us to take the
OL,12,Fappropriate action.
OL,14,F"It is important to stress that our
OL,15,Fefforts in this area don't end here
OL,16,Fand we will continue to work with our
OL,17,Fpartners in the local authority and
OL,18,Fhelp to take harmful and illegal items
OL,19,Fout of circulation.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
