OL,5,Cspace
OL,7,F"Some people might not see buying
OL,8,Fcounterfeit cigarettes or vapes as an
OL,9,Fissue, but the truth is that the
OL,10,Fproceeds from the sales of these
OL,11,Fproducts are often re-invested into
OL,12,Fmuch more serious and organised crime.
OL,14,F"By removing the profits from these
OL,15,Fgroups, we take away the power and
OL,16,Fstanding they have in the community."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
