OL,5,Cspace
OL,7,FAnneliese Hutchinson, Service Director
OL,8,Ffor Service Director Climate Change,
OL,9,FCompliance, Planning and Transport at
OL,10,FGateshead Council, added: "Removing
OL,11,Fthis quantity of illegal tobacco and
OL,12,Fvape products from the streets is a
OL,13,Fgreat outcome for Gateshead and
OL,14,Fanother example of the council and
OL,15,Fpolice working together to keep our
OL,16,Fcommunities safe.
OL,18,F"Illegal tobacco sales are very
OL,19,Fharmful as they can make smoking more
OL,20,Faccessible to children, they can also
OL,21,Ffund serious organised crime."
